STEP load
  TAKES: file: str
  GIVES: rows: List<{name: str, revenue: float}>
  MODE:  exact
  LANG:  go

STEP summarise
  TAKES: rows: List<{name: str, revenue: float}>
  GIVES: total: float
  MODE:  exact
  LANG:  go

FLOW pipeline
  load(file="customers.csv")
    -> summarise(rows)

RESOURCES
  target: go
  models: [haiku]
